  "code": "sequenceDiagram\n    participant APB as APB Write\n    participant SCHED as Scheduler\n    participant DESC as Descriptor Engine\n    participant MEM as m_axi_desc_*\n\n    APB->>SCHED: descriptor address\n    SCHED->>DESC: fetch request\n    DESC->>MEM: AXI read\n    MEM-->>DESC: 256-bit descriptor\n    DESC->>SCHED: parsed descriptor\n",
  "diagram_type": "participant size:250..400",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T04:03:34.516034",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个描述符获取的时序图。场景是：APB写入模块先把描述符地址发给调度器，然后调度器去触发描述符引擎取数据。你帮我理一下参与者和流程顺序？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB Write",
        "Scheduler",
        "Descriptor Engine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那描述符引擎是从哪里取实际数据？是直接连到存储，还是通过AXI总线？另外数据位宽是多少？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Descriptor Engine",
        "m_axi_desc_*"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "描述符引擎通过AXI去读，接口叫m_axi_desc_*。返回的是256-bit的完整描述符。解析完之后，引擎再把解析好的描述符回传给调度器。所以参与者应该是四个：APB Write、Scheduler、Descriptor Engine、还有m_axi_desc_*这个存储接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB Write",
        "Scheduler",
        "Descriptor Engine",
        "m_axi_desc_*"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我确认一下流程：第一步APB Write把descriptor address给Scheduler；第二步Scheduler发fetch request给Descriptor Engine；第三步Engine做AXI read到m_axi_desc_*；第四步存储返回256-bit descriptor；最后Engine把parsed descriptor回给Scheduler。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "descriptor address",
        "fetch request",
        "AXI read",
        "256-bit descriptor",
        "parsed descriptor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个顺序。注意最后一步是虚线返回，因为parsed descriptor是响应消息，不是新的请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "parsed descriptor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。四个参与者从左到右：APB Write、Scheduler、Descriptor Engine、m_axi_desc_*。五条消息按时间顺序排列，最后parsed descriptor用了虚线箭头表示响应。你看还有什么要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "APB Write",
        "Scheduler",
        "Descriptor Engine",
        "m_axi_desc_*"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "第三步和第四步的箭头方向好像反了？AXI read应该是Engine发给存储的请求，返回256-bit descriptor才是存储回给Engine。现在看起来两个都是Engine指向存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI read",
        "256-bit descriptor",
        "Descriptor Engine",
        "m_axi_desc_*"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修复。现在第三步是Descriptor Engine指向m_axi_desc_*的AXI read请求，第四步是m_axi_desc_*用虚线返回256-bit descriptor给Engine。这样流向就对了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXI read",
        "256-bit descriptor",
